title: Kayangan
overview: Kayangan is a realm of spirits and monsters. Habil, television host and lecturer has secrets. One, his father was a movie star. Two, the hero his father played was not fiction and Habil is heir to his father's mystic powers. Along with Ana, Bob and Zain, they assist Captain Jabbar and Vicky from the BASE task force to save citizens from Kayangan's threats.
